		<title>隨著匯價測試關鍵支撐位，美元兌日圓重新被交易者聚焦</title>
		<link>https://www.atfx.com/zh-hant/analysis/market-news/usdjpy-key-support-tested</link>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[ATFX]]></dc:creator>
		<pubDate>Tue, 25 Feb 2025 23:39:21 +0000</pubDate>
